txt.en: There is still much to do in the Vales of Anduin.
There is still more that can be done to make safe the Vales of Anduin.

Much like Enedwaith on the far side of the Misty Mountains, the Vales of Anduin consist primarily of untamed wilderness, home to simple villages, hermitsâ€™ shelters, and only few roads. Most attempts to rule this wilderness have been short-lived and have long since fallen to ruin. You have done much to aid the Wilderfolk who live here, and made more secure a traditionally unsafe region.
